data.description: Welcome to the epitome of luxurious living at 1189 Heritage Drive in Calimesa. This spectacular 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home, showcased as the model residence, redefines elegance and comfort. As you step through the front door, the main level boasts a master bedroom with a master bathroom, complete with a walk-in closet for added convenience. Another bedroom on the ground floor provides flexibility for various living arrangements. The owners have thoughtfully replaced the island in the kitchen with a significantly larger one, creating a focal point for culinary gatherings and enhancing the overall aesthetic. The attention to detail is evident in the numerous upgrades that adorn this home, from the floors to the ceilings and walls—each element carefully chosen to create an atmosphere of sophistication and warmth. Venture upstairs to discover three additional bedrooms and a spacious loft, offering versatile space for work, play, or relaxation. The layout of this home is thoughtfully designed to accommodate a variety of lifestyles. Step outside to the beautiful backyard oasis, perfect for entertaining or enjoying peaceful moments surrounded by nature. This residence is not just a home; it's a retreat. Beyond the property itself, the community provides a wealth of amenities, including a pool, spa, recreation facility, tennis courts, and a park. Embrace the convenience of resort-style living right at your doorstep. Don't miss the chance to own this exquisite home, where every detail has been carefully curated for the discerning homeowner. Let's not forget the Solar Panels that are paid off to add to the value of this lovely home. Schedule a showing today to witness firsthand the unparalleled beauty and comfort that 1189 Heritage Drive has to offer. Your dream home awaits!
